@#
# Tests for classes within namespaces
# ----------------------------------------------------------------------
#   AUTHOR:  Michael J. McLennan
#            Bell Labs Innovations for Lucent Technologies
#            mmclennan@@lucent.com
#            http://www.tcltk.com/itcl
